enable_dns_hostnames VPC lo endhuku?
ðŸ‘‰ Ee VPC lo create ayye anni EC2s ki DNS names enable cheyyadaniki.
VPC level setting idi
Okasari enable chesthe â†’ aa VPC lo unna all resources ki apply avtundi
If idi lekapothe:
EC2 ki public/private DNS names raadhu
Load Balancer, RDS, EKS problems vastayi
enable_dns_hostnames = true isthe

EC2 ki DNS name untundi
Route53 lo DNS records create cheyyagalavu
IP ki domain name map cheyyagalavu
Adhi ivvakapothe
EC2 ki DNS name undadu
Route53 record create cheyyadam panicheyyadu / issues vastayi
Simple line:
ðŸ‘‰ DNS hostnames ON unte ne IP â†’ DNS mapping possible


